data.description: This extraordinary 5-bedroom, 2-bath home nestled on three flat acres is a true gem in Centralia. With a perfect blend of elegance and comfort, and 3,038 square feet of living space, this property offers an array of features that will leave you in awe. Formal Living Room; Eat-in Kitchen; Den; Office; Upstairs Bonus Room. Primary Suite with walk-in closet, private sunroom, and patio. Primary Bathroom with Standalone Shower and Garden Tub. 3 Acres of Land inside city limits. New Laminate Flooring in Common Areas and Master Bedroom (April 2020); 2 New 40-Gallon Water Heaters (June 2021); New American Standard HVAC System (August 2022); New Carpet in 4 Bedrooms & Vinyl in Sunroom, Laundry Room, and Bonus Room (July 2023); New Appliances (October 2019); New Electrical Panel (December 2020); New Garage Door Opener (January 2021). Fixture-Based PEX Manifold. Washer, dryer, and all kitchen appliances convey.
